com.snowplowanalytics.snowplow.tracker.payload

Class SelfDescribingJson

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.snowplowanalytics.snowplow.tracker.payload.SelfDescribingJson
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Payload

    public class SelfDescribingJson
extends java.lang.Object
implements Payload
    Builds a SelfDescribingJson object which can contain two fields: - Schema: the JsonSchema path for this Json - Data: the data for this Json
